{"pageProps":{"news":{"_id":"6060be7293e7d2445c8ababc","title":"紧急召集志愿者帮忙写在救援物资！","author":"","digest":"紧急召集志愿者帮忙写在救援物资！明天上午8：30am，地点8725 Jefferson Hwy","content":"<p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/cGcYqtanUytnnCjbCHIVEyyINrJqxQN2KP3WbMWUgzz6JZVJfUZMzsY4zJJEGic87eUZatYcMrNDRDdojSmVGicg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.5629496402877698\" data-w=\"\"  /><br  /></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);\">各位同学以及学者：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;持续一周的强降雨，引发本州东南部大面积洪灾，截至目前已造成<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">至少6人死亡</span></strong>，数千房屋被侵袭，约2万居民获得营救。而首府巴吞鲁日是<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">灾情最严重的地区之一</span></strong>，虽然最严重的暴雨已经过去，但河水仍继续上涨，洪灾仍未结束，CSSA提醒各位同学，注意安全，即使天气好转，仍应尽可能避免外出。Stay dry and stay safe！</p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;David教会有一大批用于救援巴吞鲁日灾民的物资于<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">明天上午（8/17）八点半</span></strong>运到baton <span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">rouge，现紧急需要大量的志愿者帮忙卸载, 整理。“一方有难，八方支援”，是中华民族的传统美德，希望各位华人伸出援助之手，协同志愿者共同抗灾！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>*另外，欢迎各位同学关注并注册LSU志愿者</strong>：https://lsu.collegiatelink.net/form/start/106717.</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>*路易斯安娜州 志愿者</strong>：www.volunteerlouisiana.gov&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>*LSU August 2016 Flood Relief</strong>： http://www.lsu.edu/floodrelief/</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>*Red Cross</strong>：https://www.redcross.org/donate/donation</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px;\">时间：本周三（08/16）8：30 am &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px;\">地点：8725 Jefferson Hwy（从LSU开车近20分钟车程）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">交通：没有车的同学可以联系CSSA成员 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">(PS:CSSA志愿者招新中，欢迎感兴趣的同学微信联系1047302695)</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong>CSSA志愿者协会</strong></p><p><br  /></p>","url":"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMjAwNDUxMg==&mid=502456544&idx=1&sn=15c2b07d83b81aa908db1c8d006620ed#rd","thumb_media_id":"2EJIUVILHK642ZnYwwuOlhFzXXwLpqYo_zWaNampe1c","thumb_url":"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/cGcYqtanUytnnCjbCHIVEyyINrJqxQN2KQiaAteZwuDBXFVgmlvE2n9o7KejCl4OGzo4Gf19nQibJPrBu5bgkLfg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg","update_time":"2016-08-16T16:48:34.000Z","media_id":"2EJIUVILHK642ZnYwwuOlkw219t12TwgAPAnzt_eVTk","createdAt":"2021-03-28T17:35:46.648Z","updatedAt":"2021-03-28T17:35:48.316Z","__v":0,"thumb_media":{"_id":"6060be7493e7d2445c8ababd","name":"2021228-17500-s7zkem","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"hash":"2021228_17500_s7zkem_c688500710","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","size":86.1,"width":750,"height":463,"url":"/uploads/2021228_17500_s7zkem_c688500710.jpeg","formats":{"thumbnail":{"hash":"thumbnail_2021228_17500_s7zkem_c688500710","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":245,"height":151,"size":13.1,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_2021228_17500_s7zkem_c688500710.jpeg"},"small":{"hash":"small_2021228_17500_s7zkem_c688500710","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width"